data.title: Tehran Times 14.11.2023
data.meta_description: Tehran Times 14.11.2023 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document is an article from the Tehran Times discussing a statement made by Brigadier General Amir-Ali Hajizadeh, commander of Iran's IRGC Aerospace Division. Hajizadeh clarified that recent messages from the U.S. to Iran resembled pleas rather than threats, as the U.S. has been pleading with Iran to refrain from opening a new front against Israel. Hajizadeh also stated that Iran is not in a position to be threatened by anyone, as the country is at the peak of its power and prepared for all conditions.
